pulfalight.title: Display ranges for consecutively-numbered containers with AbIDs

comments.body:
Hi @m-ichelleliu -  

1. The prefixes designate location areas in our onsite stacks. 
2. We use two different numbering systems for boxes depending on their location: AbID (those with prefixes) and traditional numbers. We only began using AbID a few years ago. 

Please let me know if you have any additional questions.
